Class JsonPageTask

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.security.access.extension.authn.task.JsonPageTask
All Implemented Interfaces:
AuthenticationMechanismResultTask
Direct Known Subclasses:
JsonPageAbortTask, JsonPagePauseTask
public abstract class JsonPageTask extends Object implements AuthenticationMechanismResultTask
This class represents a task that returns an JSON page.
